sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Browser
    participant LB as OpenShift Route/LB<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Gateway as data-science-gateway<br/>(Envoy) 443/HTTPS<br/>TLS terminate
    participant EnvoyFilter as EnvoyFilter<br/>authn-filter
    participant AuthProxy as kube-auth-proxy<br/>8443/HTTPS mTLS
    participant OAuth as OpenShift OAuth<br/>443/HTTPS
    participant DashProxy as Dashboard<br/>kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/HTTPS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/HTTPS
    participant Dashboard as odh-dashboard<br/>8080/HTTP localhost
    participant Client as Client Application
    participant Kuadrant as Kuadrant AuthPolicy<br/>(Authorino)
    participant KServeProxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>sidecar 8443/HTTPS
    participant vLLM as vLLM/OVMS/MLServer<br/>8000/HTTP localhost
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/HTTPS
    participant Orchestrator as FMS Orchestrator<br/>8033/HTTP
    participant Detectors as Guardrails Detectors<br/>8080/HTTP
    participant DSP as DSP API Server<br/>8888/HTTP
    participant Argo as Argo Workflows<br/>2746/HTTP
    participant MLMD as ML Metadata<br/>8080/gRPC
    participant Trainer as Trainer Controller
    participant JobSet as JobSet API

    Note over User, Dashboard: Flow 1: Dashboard Access (Authentication)
    User->>LB: HTTPS/443
    LB->>Gateway: HTTPS/443 (TLS terminate)
    Gateway->>EnvoyFilter: Intercept request
    EnvoyFilter->>AuthProxy: 8443/HTTPS (mTLS)
    AuthProxy->>OAuth: Validate token (443/HTTPS)
    OAuth-->>AuthProxy: Auth result
    AuthProxy-->>EnvoyFilter: Allow + user headers
    EnvoyFilter-->>Gateway: HTTPRoute match
    Gateway->>DashProxy: 8443/HTTPS
    DashProxy->>K8sAPI: TokenReview + SubjectAccessReview
    K8sAPI-->>DashProxy: Authorized
    DashProxy->>Dashboard: 8080/HTTP (localhost)
    Dashboard->>K8sAPI: User token forwarded (443/HTTPS)
    Dashboard-->>User: Dashboard UI response

    Note over Client, S3: Flow 2: Model Inference (LLMInferenceService + Kuadrant)
    Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/completions<br/>HTTPS/443
    Gateway->>Kuadrant: Authentication check
    Kuadrant-->>Gateway: Auth result (UserDefined/Anonymous)
    Gateway->>KServeProxy: HTTPRoute -> predictor<br/>8443/HTTPS
    KServeProxy->>vLLM: 8000/HTTP (localhost)
    vLLM->>S3: Load model weights<br/>HTTPS/443
    S3-->>vLLM: Model artifacts
    vLLM-->>KServeProxy: Inference result (JSON/SSE)
    KServeProxy-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON/SSE Response

    Note over Client, Detectors: Flow 3: Guardrailed LLM Inference
    Client->>Orchestrator: Chat completion<br/>8090/HTTP (via gateway)
    Orchestrator->>Detectors: Input detection<br/>8080/HTTP
    Detectors-->>Orchestrator: Detection results
    Orchestrator->>vLLM: LLM inference<br/>8000/HTTP
    vLLM-->>Orchestrator: LLM output
    Orchestrator->>Detectors: Output detection<br/>8080/HTTP
    Detectors-->>Orchestrator: Detection results
    Orchestrator-->>Client: Safe response or fallback

    Note over User, MLMD: Flow 5: ML Pipeline Execution
    User->>DSP: Create pipeline run<br/>8888/HTTP (via kube-rbac-proxy)
    DSP->>Argo: Create Workflow CR<br/>2746/HTTP
    Argo->>K8sAPI: Create pipeline step pods
    K8sAPI-->>Argo: Pods scheduled
    Argo->>S3: Store artifacts<br/>443/HTTPS
    Argo->>MLMD: Track lineage<br/>8080/gRPC
    Argo-->>DSP: Run complete
    DSP-->>User: Pipeline result

    Note over User, JobSet: Flow 6: Distributed Training (TrainJob)
    User->>K8sAPI: Create TrainJob CR
    K8sAPI->>Trainer: Webhook validation<br/>9443/HTTPS
    Trainer->>K8sAPI: Resolve ClusterTrainingRuntime
    Trainer->>JobSet: Create JobSet
    Trainer->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy<br/>(per-TrainJob isolation)
    JobSet->>K8sAPI: Create Jobs -> Training Pods
    Note right of JobSet: Pods communicate via<br/>headless Service<br/>(NCCL/MPI/gRPC)
    Trainer->>K8sAPI: Progression tracking<br/>(28080/HTTP from pods)
